Based on our popular Performance Winter Mock Turtleneck, this zippered version is ideal for competition and hard training. This garment will keep you toasty warm on cold days while the 7” zipper offers extra ventilation to avoid over-heating . Made from CS Tech Fleece, the same single-sided fleece we use in our Fleece arm/knee/leg warmers.



Features:


-Made with CS Tech Fleece


-Mock turtleneck collar to keep you warm


-7” zipper for ventilation


-Unlimited number of colours


-Thumb holes on sleeves

The Champion System Technical Performance Long Sleeve Run Top is designed to maximize your workout by keeping you dry and comfortable.  Made from our exclusive microfiber CS Tech fabric, the TPT offers the fit and feel you demand from your performance clothing.


Features:



  • Constructed of CS Tech fabric.

  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+.

  • No annoying label tags at the neck

  •  Fully customisable. 

  • Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more.

APEX WeatherLite Race Jacket is an ultra lightweight, versatile, multi-sport jacket that keeps you protected from the unexpected showers or cold winds. Made with our CS WeatherLite fabric, this jacket is highly wind resistant and breathable. Rain will roll right off the fabric surface because of its DWR (durable water repellence) finish. Extremely light and packable which is ideal for runners and adventure racers who need to move fast and light.



  • Made with CS WeatherLite fabric

  • Full sublimation printing

  • Chest pocket for storage, can also be used to stow jacket

  • Storm hood with Velcro tab adjuster to allow better fit and comfort,it can be folded away when not raining

  • Elastic cuffs with thumb holes to keep your wrists warm

  • Single hand adjustable, draw-cord hem prevents weather entry and heat loss

  • Underarm vents for maximum air flow

  • Chest strap with snap button to keep the jacket in place while the front zipper is fully opened

  • Full length YKK front zip with interior storm flap for protection againstwind and rain

  • Reflective details for safety

The Champion System Apex Run Singlet is constructed of our exclusive Champion System CS AirLite fabric with strategically placed mesh side panels for even greater breathability and flatlock seams for increased comfort.


Features:



  • Constructed of CS AirLite fabric.

  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+.

  • No annoying label tags at the neck

  • Fully customisable. 

  • Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more.

  • Mens Singlet - Crew neck only

  • Women's specific-cut available - V- neck only

Designed for cold weather conditions, the thermal base layer uses the latest in heat retention technology to offer an innovative fabric that keeps heat closer to the body while at the same time wicking moisture away.  The result is increased warmth while your body remains dry.  It’s the ideal base layer when the temperature drops. Our thermal base layers can also be customized. We do not print the entire base layer, just the area below the neck. Check out the picture — where our Champion System logo appears is the area where we can print your logo.

Racerback design made with lightweight moisture wicking fabric make this performance singlet ideal for training and competition. Made from our exclusive CS Tech Lite fabric, the Bella Racerback Singlet can be fully printed with your designs and logos.



- Fully Customisable


- CS Tech Lite fabric


- Lightweight and moisture wicking


- Tagless


- Great for running, hiking, yoga, and more.

When Summer runs into Autumn and Autumn runs into Winter this lightweight water-resistant jacket will be your go to run jacket that can do it all.


Features


  • Constructed of CS WindGuard. Lightweight, water-resistant and breathable to help keep your temperature regulated
  • Draw cord that makes fine-tuning the fit easy
  • Reflective details help with low light visibility
  • Offset zipper with zipper garage to help keep your chin from getting chafed
  • Secure front zipper pockets, one with media pouchand a cord exit for your headphones,the other has an interior credit card-size Velcro pocket for convenience.
  • Elastic cuffs
  • Mesh venting in the back and the under arms to reduce over-heating

Women's Performance Run Top available in V-neck only.

The APEX Winter Shield Pro Jacket is our superior heavy winter jacket. In conjunction with our Italian suppliers, eVent Fabrics, we have created a 3 layer bonded winter fleece fabric, called Winter Shield, that keeps the rider warm in cold conditions, but is able to breathe and remove moisture under intense performance conditions. The APEX Winter Shield Pro Jacket is constructed in our new anatomic cut to maximise warmth, performance and comfort. This jacket can handle the coldest conditions.

Features

  • 3 layer bonded fleece fabric
  • 80% Polyester, 10% Elastane, 10% PTFE
  • Highly water resistant
  • Breathable fabric
  • Other panels are fitted with our CS Tech Fleece winter fabric providing excellent warmth, stretch and fit
  • Upgraded anatomic cut and panel construction
  • Ideal for cold conditions
  • Features double needle cover stitch
  • 3 rear pockets for storage with standard reflective piping, increasing visibility
  • Elasticised bottom gripper to keep jacket in place
  • >Extended lower ‘wing’ for additional protection
  • >2 way YKK zipper enabling temperature regulation
  • Features a CS Contour lycra sleeve cuff that fits under or over a gloves

Incredibly lightweight and breathable, made from our exclusive Champion System CS Helium fabric the Apex Marathon Singlet is the ideal choice for training and competitions. With a loose fit, scoop–neck design this running essential will deliver the performance and comfort you demand.


Features:



  • Constructed from CS Helium fabric

  • 100% permanent UV protection yarn able to reach UPF50+

  • No annoying label tags at the neck

  • Fully customisable. 

  • Great for clubs, events, corporate teams and more.

Our Performance Sports Bra is made from CS Contour Lycra and is designed to be the ultimate multipurpose piece for women who demand a technical high-support bra. The best part?  It can be fully customized with virtually any design using our digital sublimation printing process.

A Champion System exclusive! We've been making custom jogging suits for the Pro and National teams we sponsor and now they are available for every team and club. This high-quality garment is made from a breathable polyester fabric and features a mesh liner, high collar, a full-length concealed zipper, and two zippered front slash pockets. The best part is that it can be fully sublimated. That's right — we can take your jersey design and turn it into a matching jogging suit jacket. Great for before and after races or to just wear around town. Your team will definitely stand out and look pro! Available in both men's and women's cuts.
